race.comment: ANOTHER DAZZLER (12) finds it hard to win and has been over a year since a success. Given a let-up since racing over a bit further and is well placed this company. Likely to be beaten for early speed but will keep coming and could be value. HIGHER CALLING (8) was a debut winner then jumped straight to a Class3 and was safely held. This more suitable and stretches out ion journey. Has upside and worth another chance. HALF MOON ROO (10) found the line strongly last time and was close to the winner. Will take plenty of beating with a repeat of latest. GALACTIC LEGEND (2) was not far away last start. Reaching his peak now and placed both tries this trip. INVISIBLE TARGET (6) was only a couple away latest and looks next best.
